      "text": "iter G · IEEE Xplore embedded-JSON authors+affs\niter H · CSV double-quote-escape parser fix\niter I · Wiley citation_author_institution email CA\niter L · doi.org → local /doi/pdf/ replacement (UTPP)\n+ MDPI sup-marker · OUP CA email · Elsevier ISO\n+ JSON-LD rases · author-overlay · article-biography",
