      "x": 280,
      "y": 1515,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "rule #10 · paywalled-publisher PDF ≅ gold N/A\nrule #11 · gold-empty rases convention (95% w/ inst. kw)\nrule #12 · CJK paren suffix stripping\niter J · sentinel trail-punct + ADS pattern + same-host prefix\niter K · Elsevier PII alphanumeric match\niter P · non-institutional gold rases (job titles)",
      "originalText": "rule #10 · paywalled-publisher PDF ≅ gold N/A\nrule #11 · gold-empty rases convention (95% w/ inst. kw)\nrule #12 · CJK paren suffix stripping\niter J · sentinel trail-punct + ADS pattern + same-host prefix\niter K · Elsevier PII alphanumeric match\niter P · non-institutional gold rases (job titles)",
